(Translated by Google) Great. Pétanque tennis. Beautiful park clean and well maintained. Petanque Monday, Wednesday and Friday, afternoon and evening. Come have fun.

(Original)
Super. Pétanque tennis. Beau parc propre et bien entretenu. Pétanque lundi, mercredi et vendredi, après--midi et soirée. Venez vous amuser.
